reviews.text: Beautiful little village of around 40 houses, a river,  plenty of farms, wildlife, babbling Brooks, a school for special kids, a train station, bus stop, phone AND post box! Aprox 12 miles from Lancaster the historic Market City with links to the Pendle witches, and aprox 3 miles from Bentham, the nearest village, with several pubs, cafes, takeaways and shops.
